text:
The update Meeting API call would look something like this:
```curl --location --request PATCH '<https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/MEETING/:MEETING_ID>' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--header 'Authorization: Bearer pat-redacted' \
--data '{
    "properties": {
        "HubSpot_owner_id": "1234567890"
    }
}'```
